<li>Harry D. Harootunian, Toward Restoration (Berkeley: University of California Press, 1970), “Introduction”, pp 1 – 46; on Yoshida: chapter IV “The Culture of Action – Yoshida Shōin”, pp 184 – 219).</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li>Najita Tetsuo, The Intellectual Foundations of Modern Japanese Politics (Chicago &amp; London: University of Chicago Press), chapter 3: “Restorationism in Late Tokugawa”, pp 43 – 68.</li>
</ul>
